(974, 'Paid', 51, 84, '14', '10', 'Fish Hooky', 1607040000, '1109', 'Little Rascals S02E10 - Dickie Moore, Stymie Beard, Wheezer Hutchins and Uh-Huh Collum would much rather skip school to go fishing with Joe Cobb and Farina Hoskins. Joe offers to write them fake excuse notes, but the new teacher turns out to be Mary Kornman.', 'fish-hooky', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Fish_Hooky-800x450.jpg', 'HLS', 0, 'https://player.vimeo.com/external/825327305.m3u8?s=483d5846eae3d8034cc565aea4170d624af0aafd', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Fish Hooky', 'Little Rascals S02E10 - Dickie Moore, Stymie Beard, Wheezer Hutchins and Uh-Huh Collum would much rather skip school to go fishing with Joe Cobb and Farina Hoskins. Joe offers to write them fake excuse notes, but the new teacher turns out to be Mary Kornman.', 'No Category', 1, 0, NULL, NULL),
