(980, 'Paid', 51, 84, '14', '4', 'Choo Choo', 1607040000, '1187', 'Little Rascals S02E04 - During a stop-over in Greenpoint, some orphans slip off a train and meet the gang playing in the park. The gang has never ridden a train before so one of the older orphans, who want to run away and be cowboys, describes the food they get on board in order to switch clothes with them and get them to take their place.', 'choo-choo', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Choo_Choo-800x450.jpg', 'HLS', 0, 'https://player.vimeo.com/external/825326128.m3u8?s=335c651ce5599b7ba3ecd2c069291d717f4938b9', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Choo Choo', 'Little Rascals S02E04 - During a stop-over in Greenpoint, some orphans slip off a train and meet the gang playing in the park. The gang has never ridden a train before so one of the older orphans, who want to run away and be cowboys, describes the food they get&hellip;', 'No Category', 1, 0, NULL, NULL),
