(2187, 'Paid', 77, 127, '16', '45', 'The Dish Ran Away with the Spoon', 1598918400, '449', 'Dishes and utensils wash, dry, and stack themselves. A duster plays a silverware box like a piano while a salt-pepper-and-sugar set sings. The spoon proposes to the dish (interrupted by a cry from a baby spoon), then plays percussion on some pans and jam jars. Some teacups do a can-can, then a centipede-like conga line. The Swiss cheese yodels. The blueing sings \\\"Am I Blue?,\\\" joined by a potato crying from all its eyes. An egg dances, slips on some lard, hatches, and sings \\\"Young and Healthy.\\\" A lump of dough rises like a ghost and dances over to a packet of yeast, which it mixes into water and drinks, then grows, a la Jekyll and Hyde. It threatens the dish; some utensils fight back, lobbing canned goods from a spatula catapult. More attacks with cheese graters, popcorn, a rolling pin, and an electric fan, turn the dough into muffins, a bundt cake, a pie, and waffles.', 'the-dish-ran-away-with-the-spoon', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/The_Dish_Ran_Away_with_the_Spoon-1-800x450.jpg', 'HLS', 0, 'https://cdnapi.bamboo-video.com/api/entry/0_taosspai/flavors/playlist.m3u8?iid=628d30305b36f9556200b806', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Dish Ran Away with the Spoon', 'Dishes and utensils wash, dry, and stack themselves. A duster plays a silverware box like a piano while a salt-pepper-and-sugar set sings. The spoon proposes to the dish (interrupted by a cry from a baby spoon), then plays percussion on some pans and jam jars. Some teacups do a can-can,&hellip;', 'No Category', 1, 0, NULL, NULL),
