(2204, 'Paid', 77, 128, '16', '73', 'What Price Porky', 1598832000, '445', 'Porky tries to feed his chickens, but some ducks steal the corn he puts out, then declare war. The battle rages, with the ducks against the chickens, sometimes in wing-to-wing combat, but also aerial attacks, and Porky finally turning the tide with his machine gun improvised from a wringer washer and a bag of corn. But the ducks still get the last laugh.', 'what-price-porky', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/What_Price_Porky-800x450.jpg', 'HLS', 0, 'https://cdnapi.bamboo-video.com/api/entry/0_1n8j9w9d/flavors/playlist.m3u8?iid=628d30305b36f9556200b806', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'What Price Porky', 'Porky tries to feed his chickens, but some ducks steal the corn he puts out, then declare war. The battle rages, with the ducks against the chickens, sometimes in wing-to-wing combat, but also aerial attacks, and Porky finally turning the tide with his machine gun improvised from a wringer washer&hellip;', 'No Category', 1, 0, NULL, NULL),
(2205, 'Paid', 77, 128, '16', '72', 'Golddigers of ’49', 1598832000, '493', 'The gold rush. Beans finds gold in the mountains and rushes into town with the news. Soon, everyone (except Porky\\\'s daughter Little Kitty, who Beans fancies) has rushed out to the mountains, but because Porky takes Beans in his car (!), they get there first. Porky finds a gold nugget, then keeps taking it from his pocket. Beans finds a treasure chest that contains a book, \\\"How to Find Gold.\\\" A bad guy spots a sack near Porky\\\'s equipment and lassos it; Porky tells Beans that if he retrieves the sack, he can have Porky\\\'s daughter. Beans gives chase in Porky\\\'s car; there\\\'s a shootout. The car runs out of gas, so Beans refills it with moonshine and it takes off like a shot. He snares the bad guy, the sack, and Porky and races back to town. Porky gives Beans his daughter\\\'s hand and reveals the contents of the sack.', 'golddigers-of-49', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Golddigers_of_49.jpg', 'HLS', 0, 'https://cdnapi.bamboo-video.com/api/entry/0_ev7g1nty/flavors/playlist.m3u8?iid=628d30305b36f9556200b806', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Golddigers of ’49', 'The gold rush. Beans finds gold in the mountains and rushes into town with the news. Soon, everyone (except Porky\\\'s daughter Little Kitty, who Beans fancies) has rushed out to the mountains, but because Porky takes Beans in his car (!), they get there first. Porky finds a gold nugget,&hellip;', 'No Category', 1, 0, NULL, NULL);
