(2, 2, '17', 'The Dark: Forever Winter', 'the-dark-forever-winter', 'The Second Installment of The Dark Anthology Series: It is the end of days, and the Forever Winter has begun. Surviving alone in the wilderness, 15-year-old Lizzy is a child hardened by her experiences in a world that is quickly going to hell.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/5039-The-Dark-Forever-Winter_1920x1080-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Dark: Forever Winter', 'The Second Installment of The Dark Anthology Series: It is the end of days, and the Forever Winter has begun. Surviving alone in the wilderness, 15-year-old Lizzy is a child hardened by her experiences in a world that is quickly going to hell.', 'Action,Drama,faith,Originals,Series,the dark,Thriller', 1, 0),
