(13, 2, '17', 'The Chosen', 'the-chosen', 'The first-ever-multi-season TV show about the life of Jesus. Created outside of the Hollywood system, The Chosen allows us to see Him through the eyes of those who knew him. No matter where you are at in your journey with Jesus Christ, this TV show is for you.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/The-Chosen-Logo-Jesus-Jonathan-Roumie.jp_-scaled-1-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Chosen', 'The first-ever-multi-season TV show about the life of Jesus. Created outside of the Hollywood system, The Chosen allows us to see Him through the eyes of those who knew him. No matter where you are at in your journey with Jesus Christ, this TV show is for you.', 'Drama,Easter,faith,Free Shows,New Episodes', 1, 0),
