(99, 2, '', 'How Should We Then Live?', 'how-should-we-then-live', 'How Should We Then Live? How Should We Then Live: The Rise and Decline of Western Thought and Culture is a major Christian cultural and historical documentary film series and book. The book was written by presuppositionalist theologian Francis A. Schaeffer and first published in 1976.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/howthenshallwelive-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'How Should We Then Live?', 'How Should We Then Live? How Should We Then Live: The Rise and Decline of Western Thought and Culture is a major Christian cultural and historical documentary film series and book. The book was written by presuppositionalist theologian Francis A. Schaeffer and first published in 1976.', 'Documentaries,Educational', 1, 0),
(100, 2, '16', 'Batgirl (1967)', 'batgirl-1967', 'Before Batgirl, who was already a high-kicking sidekick on Batman, soared into a show of her own, she starred in an unaired pilot that collected dust in some dark corner of the Gotham City library for years. Her mysterious origins have been revealed by the video surfacing on that ingenious thing we call the Internet. Leap onto the Batgirl cycle, let your cape ripple in the wind and take a ride through Barbara Gordon\\\'s transformation secrets.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/batgir-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Batgirl (1967)', 'Before Batgirl, who was already a high-kicking sidekick on Batman, soared into a show of her own, she starred in an unaired pilot that collected dust in some dark corner of the Gotham City library for years. Her mysterious origins have been revealed by the video surfacing on that ingenious thing we call the Internet. Leap onto the Batgirl cycle, let your cape ripple in the wind and take a ride through Barbara Gordon\\\'s transformation secrets.', 'Comedy,Free Shows,Series', 1, 0),
(101, 2, '', 'Creation Seminar Series: Dr. Kent Hovind', 'creation-seminar-series-dr-kent-hovind', 'Award Winning Creation Seminar Series\nThis series has over 18-hours of scientific evidence proving the Bible’s accuracy, and the dangers of evolutionism.\nThis award-winning DVD video series discusses topics:\nDVD #1 The Age of the Earth\nDVD #2 Garden of Eden\nDVD #3 Dinosaurs and the Bible\nDVD #4 Lies in the Textbooks\nDVD #5 The Dangers of Evolution\nDVD #6 The Hovind Theory\nDVD #7 Questions and Answers session part 1 & 2\nYou can now see them here for free on ReDiscover Television', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/kenthovind-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Creation Seminar Series: Dr. Kent Hovind', 'Award Winning Creation Seminar Series\nThis series has over 18-hours of scientific evidence proving the Bible’s accuracy, and the dangers of evolutionism.\nThis award-winning DVD video series discusses topics:\nDVD #1 The Age of the Earth\nDVD #2 Garden of Eden\nDVD #3 Dinosaurs and the Bible\nDVD #4 Lies in the Textbooks\nDVD #5 The Dangers of Evolution\nDVD #6 The Hovind Theory\nDVD #7 Questions and Answers session part 1 & 2\nYou can now see them here for free on ReDiscover Television', 'Educational', 1, 0),
(102, 2, '', 'The Trials & Testimony of the Early Church', 'the-trials-testimony-of-the-early-church', 'The Trials & Testimony of the Early Church: One of the most popular series from the Christian history collection. This gripping series of six programs, produced in consultation with an international team of scholars, takes you to the actual locations to show what the early church was like, how it spread, and the persecution it endured. Host for the award-winning series is Steve Bell. Actors Nigel Goodwin, Russell Boulter, and Jane Campion dramatize leading figures and events from the early church.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/trialsandtestimony-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Trials & Testimony of the Early Church', 'The Trials & Testimony of the Early Church: One of the most popular series from the Christian history collection. This gripping series of six programs, produced in consultation with an international team of scholars, takes you to the actual locations to show what the early church was like, how it spread, and the persecution it endured. Host for the award-winning series is Steve Bell. Actors Nigel Goodwin, Russell Boulter, and Jane Campion dramatize leading figures and events from the early church.', 'Educational', 1, 0),
(103, 2, '14', 'Mighty Mouse', 'mighty-mouse', 'Mighty Mouse is an American animated anthropomorphic superhero mouse character created by the Terrytoons studio for 20th Century Fox. The character was originally called Super Mouse, and made his debut in the 1942 short The Mouse of Tomorrow. The name was changed to Mighty Mouse in his eighth film, 1944\\\'s The Wreck of the Hesperus, and the character went on to star in 80 theatrical shorts, concluding in 1961 with Cat Alarm.', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Mighty-Mouse-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mighty Mouse', 'Mighty Mouse is an American animated anthropomorphic superhero mouse character created by the Terrytoons studio for 20th Century Fox. The character was originally called Super Mouse, and made his debut in the 1942 short The Mouse of Tomorrow. The name was changed to Mighty Mouse in his eighth film, 1944\\\'s The Wreck of the Hesperus, and the character went on to star in 80 theatrical shorts, concluding in 1961 with Cat Alarm.', 'Free Kid Stuff,Kid Programs', 1, 0),
(104, 2, '', 'Rediscovering God in America with Newt Gingrich', 'rediscovering-god-in-america-with-newt-gingrich', 'Take a walk through our Nation\\\'s Capital with Speaker Newt Gingrich and his wife, Callista Gingrich. From the National Archives to Arlington National Cemetery, this film illustrates the importance of our Creator to our nation\\\'s founders and their successors. Hear from best-selling author Walter Isaacson, Attornery General Edwin Meese III, authors and historians H.W. Brands and Douglas Brinkley, Ambassador and author Michael Novak and Wallbuilders President David Barton. Based on the New York Times bestseller, REDISCOVERING GOD IN AMERICA reminds us all that America is indeed \\\"One Nation Under God.\\\"', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/rediscoveringGod-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Rediscovering God in America with Newt Gingrich', 'Take a walk through our Nation\\\'s Capital with Speaker Newt Gingrich and his wife, Callista Gingrich. From the National Archives to Arlington National Cemetery, this film illustrates the importance of our Creator to our nation\\\'s founders and their successors. Hear from best-selling author Walter Isaacson, Attornery General Edwin Meese III, authors and historians H.W. Brands and Douglas Brinkley, Ambassador and author Michael Novak and Wallbuilders President David Barton. Based on the New York Times bestseller, REDISCOVERING GOD IN AMERICA reminds us all that America is indeed \\\"One Nation Under God.\\\"', 'Documentaries,fourth of july', 1, 0),
(105, 2, '', 'Christian Apologetics', 'christian-apologetics', 'Christian Apologetics with Brian Edwards - 25 episodes covering all aspects of Christian Apologetics such as:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Authentic Christ</li>\n 	<li>Flood Geology</li>\n 	<li>Scripture Under Scrutiny and more...</li>\n</ul>', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/apologetics-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Christian Apologetics', 'Christian Apologetics with Brian Edwards - 25 episodes covering all aspects of Christian Apologetics such as:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Authentic Christ</li>\n 	<li>Flood Geology</li>\n 	<li>Scripture Under Scrutiny and more...</li>\n</ul>', 'Educational,Sermons', 1, 0),
(106, 2, '', 'The Book of Revelation with Steven Anderson', 'the-book-of-revelation-with-steven-anderson', 'Pastor Steven Anderson from Faithful Word Baptist Church in Tempe, Arizona takes us through a very unique perspective on the Book of Revelation. Going chapter by chapter, he leaves no stone unturned in this 22 part series. Directed by Paul Wittenberger', NULL, 'https://www.rediscovertelevision.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/revelation-800x450.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Book of Revelation with Steven Anderson', 'Pastor Steven Anderson from Faithful Word Baptist Church in Tempe, Arizona takes us through a very unique perspective on the Book of Revelation. Going chapter by chapter, he leaves no stone unturned in this 22 part series. Directed by Paul Wittenberger', 'Sermons', 1, 0);
